# Sūra XXVI.: Shu‘arāa, or The Poets.

### Section 6

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_105.gif)

105. Ka<u>thth</u>abat qawmu noo<u>h</u>in almursaleen**a**

105\. The people of Noah rejected  
The apostles.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_106.gif)

106. I<u>th</u> q<u>a</u>la lahum akhoohum noo<u>h</u>un al<u>a</u>
tattaqoon**a**

106\. Behold, their brother Noah  
Said to them: "Will ye not  
Fear (God)?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_107.gif)

107. Innee lakum rasoolun ameen**un**

107\. "I am to you an apostle  
Worthy of all trust:

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_108.gif)

108. Fa**i**ttaqoo All<u>a</u>ha waa<u>t</u>eeAAoon**i**

108\. "So fear God, and obey me.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_109.gif)

109. Wam<u>a</u> as-alukum AAalayhi min ajrin in ajriya ill<u>a</u>
AAal<u>a</u> rabbi alAA<u>a</u>lameen**a**

109\. "No reward do I ask  
Of you for it: my reward  
Is only from the Lord  
Of the Worlds:

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_110.gif)

110. Fa**i**ttaqoo All<u>a</u>ha waa<u>t</u>eeAAoon**i**

110\. "So fear God, and obey me."

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_111.gif)

111. Q<u>a</u>loo anu/minu laka wa**i**ttabaAAaka
al-ar<u>th</u>aloon**a**

111\. They said: "Shall we  
Believe in thee when it is  
The meanest that follow thee?"

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_112.gif)

112. Q<u>a</u>la wam<u>a</u> AAilmee bim<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>noo
yaAAmaloon**a**

112\. He said: "And what  
Do I know as to  
What they do?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_113.gif)

113. In <u>h</u>is<u>a</u>buhum ill<u>a</u> AAal<u>a</u> rabbee law
tashAAuroon**a**

113\. "Their account is only  
With my Lord, if ye  
Could (but) understand.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_114.gif)

114. Wam<u>a</u> an<u>a</u> bi<u>ta</u>ridi almu/mineen**a**

114\. "I am not one to drive away  
Those who believe.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_115.gif)

115. In an<u>a</u> ill<u>a</u> na<u>th</u>eerun mubeen**un**

115\. "I am sent only  
To warn plainly in public."

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_116.gif)

116. Q<u>a</u>loo la-in lam tantahi y<u>a</u> noo<u>h</u>u latakoonanna
mina almarjoomeen**a**

116\. They said: "If thou  
Desist not, O Noah!  
Thou shalt be stoned  
(to death)."

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_117.gif)

117. Q<u>a</u>la rabbi inna qawmee ka<u>thth</u>aboon**i**

117\. He said: "O my Lord!  
Truly my people have  
Rejected me.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_118.gif)

118. Fa**i**fta<u>h</u> baynee wabaynahum fat<u>h</u>an wanajjinee waman
maAAiya mina almu/mineen**a**

118\. "Judge thou, then, between me  
And them openly, and deliver  
Me and those of the Believers  
Who are with me."

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_119.gif)

119. Faanjayn<u>a</u>hu waman maAAahu fee alfulki almashhoon**i**

119\. So We delivered him  
And those with him,  
In the Ark filled  
(With all creatures).

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_120.gif)

120. Thumma aghraqn<u>a</u> baAAdu alb<u>a</u>qeen**a**

120\. Thereafter We drowned those  
Who remained behind.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_121.gif)

121. Inna fee <u>tha</u>lika la<u>a</u>yatan wam<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>na
aktharuhum mu/mineen**a**

121\. Verily in this is a Sign:  
But most of them  
Do not believe.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_122.gif)

122. Wa-inna rabbaka lahuwa alAAazeezu a**l**rra<u>h</u>eem**u**

122\. And verily thy Lord  
Is He, the Exalted in Might,  
Most Merciful.

